title: Colin Kaepernick: Can success be rediscovered against Green Bay?
text:
Photo: Christian Petersen, Getty Images Colin Kaepernick threw for 67 yards against the Cardinals, almost one-fifth of his career average against Green Bay. Colin Kaepernick threw for 67 yards against the Cardinals, almost...
Thirty-two months ago, Colin Kaepernick rushed for 181 yards, threw for 263 yards and had four total touchdowns in a 45-31 divisional-playoff win over the Packers.
